inclusion.criterion: Thai women aged 20-45 years at the time of HPV vaccination
inclusion.label: met

inclusion.criterion: Received at least 1 dose of bivalent or quadrivalent HPV vaccine at least 5 years ago
inclusion.label: met

inclusion.criterion: Willing to provide written informed consent and receive Pap smear & HPV genotyping
inclusion.label: met

exclusion.criterion: History of hysterectomy or excisional treatment of the cervix
exclusion.label: not_met

notes: A 54-year-old woman with abnormal cervical squamous intraepithelial/glandular lesion and HPV 16 positivity, who smokes and drinks alcohol frequently.
